history.content:
Here's the thing....

You should be able to attend the section you are enrolled in.  Faculty are often flexible particularly about which discussion --less so which lab -- you actually attend.  That being said, it is their call.  The person who teaches the class gets to decide.  Anybody else who tells you something is just making it up -- maybe making it up based on what the same instructor did in the past which would be the best estimate but even then that instructor could change their mind based on their previous experience or even based on a whim.
